prompt_template:
Analyze the promotional lift results. For each campaign, summarize the revenue and unit lift, identify top-performing SKUs, and comment on campaign effectiveness.

Promo Results:
{% for row in dsp_data %}
- {{ row.campaign_name }} ({{ row.start_date }} to {{ row.end_date }}): +${{ row.revenue_lift | int }} revenue, +{{ row.unit_lift | int }} units ({{ row.skus_in_promo }} SKUs)
{% endfor %}

Return a JSON object with: narrative_text (markdown summary of overall performance and insights, max 150 words).
